text: Roderick Moores (born April 9, 1949) was a Canadian politician. He represented the electoral district of Carbonear in the Newfoundland and Labrador House of Assembly from 1975 to 1982. He was a member of the Liberal Reform Party.Encyclopedia of Newfoundland and Labrador He was born at Carbonear. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Liberal Party of Newfoundland and Labrador MHAs Category:Newfoundland Reform Liberal Party MHAs
